      "review_summary": "The PR allows `openai/gpt-5.3-codex-spark` through Codex harness-selected OpenAI routes while keeping native OpenAI API-host and direct API routes suppressed, with docs and regression coverage.\n\nPR surface: Source +502, Tests +1210, Docs +1. Total +1713 across 19 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. at source level: current main unconditionally suppresses `openai/gpt-5.3-codex-spark` before harness recovery can resolve it. I did not rerun a live Spark turn locally, but the PR body and latest proof check include redacted after-fix live catalog/gateway evidence.",
